           <p> Enrollment deposit payments after the deadline will not be processed and your offer for admission will stand annulled.</p>
           <p> Sincerely, </p>
           <p><strong> FLAME University Admissions Committee </strong> </p>
            </div>
            
         <div class="tab-container">
     <apex:form >            
     
      <table style="font-family: Cambria,Georgia, serif; font-size:14px; width:40%; border:1px solid #666; padding:10px; border-collapse:collapse border-spacing: none;" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
        
        <tr> 
             <td style="border:1px solid #666;padding:10px;"> <apex:outputLabel value="Enrollment Deposit Amount :"/></td>
             <td align="left" width="10%" style="padding:10px;border:1px solid #666;">INR&nbsp;<apex:outputField value="{!App.Program__r.Enrollment_Deposit_Amount__c}"/></td>
        </tr>
       
